\end_layout

\end_inset

the hard work having been the previous identification of the form of the
 question.
 The output for 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset


\emph on
Who ate my lunch?
\emph default

\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 is:
\end_layout

